examples: Are you a member of the American Athletic Association?
Since you're such an athletic person, you may wish to consider joining.

definitions.definition: Having a muscular , well developed body , being in shape.
examples: You have such an athletic build—you must work out regularly.

definitions.definition: An attribute of a motion or play which requires fine physical ability.
examples: The center fielder made an athletic play to snatch the ball from over the fence.

definitions.definition: Of a level in a Super Mario game: with an emphasis on platforming challenge, often involving precise jumps between floating platforms above a bottomless pit , and having upbeat background music .

main_definition: ( not comparable ) Having to do with athletes .
